NK040(thi)025:1: // mkha' 'gro'i tshogs mchod tshogs gnyis bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun bzhugs so //
NK040(thi)025:2: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK040(thi)025:3: gcod kyi sgo nas tshogs mchod byed par 'dod na /
NK040(thi)025:4: tshogs kyi zhal zas bza' ba sha mar zla rgyas
NK040(thi)025:5: pa la sogs pa rang gi mdun g.yas su bshams
NK040(thi)025:6: / ja chang sogs dza gad btung ba'i rigs thams cad g.yon du bshams /
NK040(thi)025:7: de nas rnal 'byor pa rnams gral du 'khod la /
NK040(thi)025:8: thun mong gi skyabs 'gro sems bskyed bya ba ni /
NK040(thi)025:9: ma mi min ye shes mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)025:11: ces sogs kyi rnam dag bya zhing /
NK040(thi)025:12: phata phatah brjod pas nam mkha' sgo 'byed bya zhing /
NK040(thi)025:13: dbyings rigs bsres de nas ngag tu /
NK040(thi)025:14: phatahphatah skad cig gis stong pa chos sku'i ngang las
NK040(thi)025:15: rang gi rnam par shes pa'i ngo bo rje btsun
NK040(thi)025:16: ma sku mdog dmar mo gri gug thod khrag 'dzin
NK040(thi)025:18: de nas tshogs byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK040(thi)025:20: sarba dra pyam shwa d+ha ni h'u phatah yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor /
NK040(thi)025:22: de'i steng du kam kam kam las thod pa'i sgyed pu gdong pa phyir bstan cing /
NK040(thi)025:23: ltag pa nang du bstan pa gsum gyi steng du /
NK040(thi)025:24: +aa las b+han+d+ha k+aa pa la phyi dkar la nang dmar ba /
NK040(thi)025:25: yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du /
NK040(thi)025:27: rang gi ro de nyid gcig tu 'dres pa las /
NK040(thi)025:30: rus pa'i gram khrod chen po gcig tu gyur /
NK040(thi)025:36: rdzas rnams 'od du zhu ba'i rlang pa sprin bzhin du 'khrigs pa las /
NK040(thi)025:37: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor rdo rje phyed pas mtshan pa'i rtse mo +aahmh'u s+w+aa h+aa /
NK040(thi)025:38: mum lam mam pyam t+yam gis mtshan pa dang bcas
NK040(thi)025:39: pa las 'od zer 'phros pas sangs rgyas dang byang
NK040(thi)025:40: chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi thugs chos nyid kyi
NK040(thi)025:41: bdud rtsi chu rgyun bsdus pas /
NK040(thi)025:43: yi ge 'bru bcu 'od du zhu ste rdo rjer thim /
NK040(thi)025:44: rdo rje 'od du zhu ste zla ba la thim /
NK040(thi)025:46: dam tshig bdud rtsi dang lhan cig du 'dres pa las /
NK040(thi)025:47: b+han+d+ha ltems kyis gang bar gyur /
NK040(thi)025:48: +aahmh'u ma h+aa sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK040(thi)025:49: +aahmh'u ma h+aa b+ha ling+ta te dz+wa b+ha ling+ta b+ha
NK040(thi)025:50: la b+ha ti gu h+ya sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa
NK040(thi)025:52: de nas tshogs spyan 'dren cing mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK040(thi)025:55: rol mo dbyangs dang bcas pas 'di skad do //
NK040(thi)025:56: h'uh gnas mkha' dbyings rnam dag pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)025:57: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK040(thi)025:58: chos sku longs sku sprul sku gsum //
NK040(thi)025:59: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun gsum //
NK040(thi)025:60: khyed sangs rgyas byang sems tshogs bcas rnams //
NK040(thi)025:62: tshogs kyi mchod pa yar bzhes la //
NK040(thi)025:63: mchog thun mong dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK040(thi)025:64: gnas 'og min chos dbyings pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)025:65: yum chen shes rab phar phyin man chad nas //
NK040(thi)025:66: rtsa ba'i bla ma yan chad kyis //
NK040(thi)025:67: khyed ma rgyud dpa' mo'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK040(thi)025:69: tshogs kyi mchod pa dam pa yar bzhes la //
NK040(thi)025:70: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK040(thi)025:71: gnas bya rgod phung po'i ri bo nas //
NK040(thi)025:72: bcom ldan sh+aakya thub pa man chad nas //
NK040(thi)025:73: rtsa ba'i bla ma yan chad kyi //
NK040(thi)025:74: khyod pho brgyud dpa' bo'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK040(thi)025:77: tshogs kyi mchod pa dam pa yar bzhes la //
NK040(thi)025:78: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK040(thi)025:79: gnas bkra shis glang lung gi dgon pa na //
NK040(thi)025:80: sras rgyal ba don 'grub man chad nas //
NK040(thi)025:81: da lta rtsa ba'i bla ma yan chad nas //
NK040(thi)025:82: khyed sras nyams myong gi brgyud pa 'khor dang bcas //
NK040(thi)025:84: gnas spyi gtsug nyi zla'i gdan steng nas //
NK040(thi)025:85: drin chen rtsa ba'i bla ma rdo rje 'chang //
NK040(thi)025:86: khyod bka' brgyud bla ma'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK040(thi)025:88: gnas gnyan sa ri khrod kyi dgon pa grogs snyems thag chod pa sprul pa'i //
NK040(thi)025:89: khyed dpa' bo dpa' mo'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK040(thi)025:90: gnas 'dir sogs yul nyi shu rtsa bzhi'i gnas mchog nas //
NK040(thi)025:91: yi dam rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams //
NK040(thi)025:92: khyod mkha' 'gro shugs 'gro'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK040(thi)025:94: gnas bsil ba tshal gyi dur khrod nas //
NK040(thi)025:95: chos skyong ma mgon lcam dral sogs //
NK040(thi)025:96: khyed dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK040(thi)025:98: tshogs khang gzhal yas pho brang 'di //
NK040(thi)025:99: o rgyan gnas su byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)025:100: 'dir tshogs skal ldan pho mo rnams //
NK040(thi)025:101: dpa' bo dpa' mor byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)025:102: rin chen la sogs snod rnams kun //
NK040(thi)025:104: zhal zas tshogs kyi mchod pa 'di //
NK040(thi)025:105: zag med bdud rtsir byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)025:106: byin rlabs thugs rje rgyun ma chad //
NK040(thi)025:107: mchog thun mong gnyis kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK040(thi)025:108: rkyen phyi nang gnyis kyi bar chad sol //
NK040(thi)025:109: ma h+aa su kha a la la ho /
NK040(thi)025:110: de nas sman mchod bya ba la /
NK040(thi)025:111: thog mar sman gyi che ba brjod pa ni /
NK040(thi)025:113: rang byung gdod nas rnam dag pa'i //
NK040(thi)025:114: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK040(thi)025:115: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK040(thi)025:116: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK040(thi)025:117: rgyud lnga'i sems can kun sgrol phyir //
NK040(thi)025:118: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK040(thi)025:119: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK040(thi)025:120: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen dang //
NK040(thi)025:121: khro bo'i rgyal po mtha' yas dang //
NK040(thi)025:122: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rnams kyi //
NK040(thi)025:123: lha dang lha mo gsang ba'i bdag /
NK040(thi)025:124: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskul ba'i tshogs //
NK040(thi)025:125: 'di ni sngon gyi dam tshig go //
NK040(thi)025:126: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK040(thi)025:127: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang nyid 'di //
NK040(thi)025:128: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK040(thi)025:129: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK040(thi)025:130: phul ba'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK040(thi)025:131: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kha hi /
NK040(thi)025:133: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)025:134: pha rol phyin ma sh+aakya'i rgyal po dang //
NK040(thi)025:135: smra ba'i seng ge dang ni 'phags pa lha //
NK040(thi)025:136: sgrol ma ma h+aa su ka sid+d+hi dang //
NK040(thi)025:137: ka ma shi la bsod nams bla ma dang //
NK040(thi)025:138: ma cig lab sgron khu sgom chos seng dang //
NK040(thi)025:139: dol pa zang thal rgya nag gcer bu dang //
NK040(thi)025:140: sangs rgyas rab brtan rtog ldan dge slong dang //
NK040(thi)025:141: sangs rgyas gnyan ston zhen med ras pa dang //
NK040(thi)025:142: chos kyi seng+ge badz+ra seng+ha dang //
NK040(thi)025:143: pra dz+ny+aa gu ru badz+ra sh+ri pa dang //
NK040(thi)025:144: ga ga badz+ra shi la ke tu dang //
NK040(thi)025:145: dz+ny+aa na ke tu gu na sh+ri dang ni //
NK040(thi)025:146: bya btang chen po kun dga' 'bum pa dang //
NK040(thi)025:147: bsod nams 'bum pa sh+aakya 'od zer dang //
NK040(thi)025:148: ke tu seng+ha nam mkha' rdo rje dang //
NK040(thi)025:149: ga ga ma ti ka la badz+ra dang //
NK040(thi)025:150: dbang drag rgya mtsho chos skyong rgya mtsho dang //
NK040(thi)025:151: klong gsal snying po chos nyid rgya mtsho dang //
NK040(thi)025:152: bkra shis phun tshogs nam mkha' rgya mtsho dang //
NK040(thi)025:153: 'ju bla pad chos sangs rgyas grags pa dang //
NK040(thi)025:154: nam mkha' chos skyong 'jig med bsam gtan dang //
NK040(thi)025:155: kun bzang rnam rgyal rat+na gu ru dang //
NK040(thi)025:156: chos kyi rgya mtsho rdo rje legs bshad rtsal //
NK040(thi)025:157: rtsa ba brgyud sogs sam yang na man ngag don brgyud ltar na /
NK040(thi)025:158: nam mkha' rgya mtsho'i rjes su /
NK040(thi)025:159: dri med zhing skyong tshe dbang mchog grub dang //
NK040(thi)025:160: nges don dbang po 'gyur med bstan 'dzin dang //
NK040(thi)025:161: chos kyi blo gros kun bzang 'gyur med dang //
NK040(thi)025:162: chos kyi rgya mtsho rdo rje legs bshad rtsal //
NK040(thi)025:163: rtsa bar brgyud pa'i bla ma bcas pa la //
NK040(thi)025:164: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK040(thi)025:165: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK040(thi)025:166: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kha hi /
NK040(thi)025:167: chos dbyings dur khrod 'bar ba'i pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)025:168: zhi khro rabs 'byams rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs //
NK040(thi)025:169: gsang sngags phyi nang brgyud pa'i lha tshogs la //
NK040(thi)025:170: rnam dag bdud thugs sarba pany+tsa rnam dag u rgyan bkod pa'i pho brang du //
NK040(thi)025:171: mkha' 'gro'i gtso mo rdo rje rnal 'byor ma //
NK040(thi)025:172: rigs bzhi mkha' 'gro shugs 'gro 'khor bcas la //
NK040(thi)025:173: rnam dag thugs rjes brtser dgongs sarba pany+tsa bka' dang dam tshig gnyen po'i pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)025:174: 'jig rten dang ni 'jig rten las 'das pa'i //
NK040(thi)025:175: bstan pa bsrung mdzad chos skyong srung ma la //
NK040(thi)025:176: rnam dag thugs rjes sarba pany+tsa a mri ta la kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK040(thi)025:177: ces bzed zhal du sbreng zhing 'bul lo //
NK040(thi)025:179: dang po bka' brgyud bla ma la 'bul ba ni /
NK040(thi)025:180: bcad khams gcig bcad la bzed zhal du bcug la chang gis bran te /
NK040(thi)025:181: slob mas btab tshul bya zhing /
NK040(thi)025:182: slob dpon gyis rol mo dang bcas pas /
NK040(thi)025:183: kye gzigs shig mdzes ldan dam pa'i chos //
NK040(thi)025:184: de la rnam rtog byed mi rung //
NK040(thi)025:185: bram ze khyi dang gdol pa gsum //
NK040(thi)025:186: rang bzhin gcig tu dgongs te rol //
NK040(thi)025:187: rin thang med la legs 'ong chos //
NK040(thi)025:188: 'dod chags dri ma dang rnam par dag /
NK040(thi)025:189: gzung dang 'dzin pa kun spang pa //
NK040(thi)025:190: de bzhin nyid la bdag phyag 'tshal //
NK040(thi)025:193: zhal zas tshogs kyi mchod pa 'di //
NK040(thi)025:194: stong gsum tsam du dpe blangs bzhin //
NK040(thi)025:195: srid gsum tsam du bkang byas pa //
NK040(thi)025:196: ri rab tsam du 'u ru ru //
NK040(thi)025:197: rgya mtsho tsam du me re re //
NK040(thi)025:198: gling bzhi tsam du kyi li li //
NK040(thi)025:199: rtsa ba'i bla ma bka' drin can //
NK040(thi)025:200: brgyud pa'i bla ma byin brlabs can //
NK040(thi)025:201: 'dren pa'i bla ma thugs rje can //
NK040(thi)025:202: khyod tshogs la dga' bas tshogs la rol //
NK040(thi)025:203: la la phyi yi tshogs la rol //
NK040(thi)025:204: la la nang gi tshogs la rol //
NK040(thi)025:205: la la gsang ba'i tshogs la rol //
NK040(thi)025:206: la la de bzhin nyid kyi tshogs la rol //
NK040(thi)025:207: a la la ste tshogs la rol //
NK040(thi)025:208: a la la ste bzhes su gsol //
NK040(thi)025:209: phyi snod 'jig rten nang bcud 'dod yon lnga //
NK040(thi)025:210: phyi yi tshogs su 'bul lo rol par bzhes //
NK040(thi)025:211: gzugs phung snod du sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga //
NK040(thi)025:212: nang gi tshogs su 'bul lo dgyes par bzhes //
NK040(thi)025:213: dbang po'i snod du dug lnga ye shes lnga //
NK040(thi)025:214: gsang ba'i tshogs su 'bul lo stong par bzhes //
NK040(thi)025:215: phyi nang gsang ba'i tshogs kyi mchod pa 'di //
NK040(thi)025:216: gnyis med chos dbyings ngang du mnyam par bzhes //
NK040(thi)025:217: ma h+aa su kha sa ma ya ho /
NK040(thi)025:218: grub thob gcod kyi brgyud pa //
NK040(thi)025:219: rtogs ldan nyams kyi brgyud pa //
NK040(thi)025:220: bka' brgyud bla ma yab sras sogs rig 'dzin brgyud
NK040(thi)025:221: pa'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams kyi zhal du g+ha
NK040(thi)025:222: na tsa kra puts+tsha me g+ha kha kha kh+aa hi
NK040(thi)025:223: / bdag gi dam tshig chags nyams thams cad byang zhing dag nas /
NK040(thi)025:224: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus pa stsal du gsol /
NK040(thi)025:225: zhes bla ma'i gtor mar 'bul lo //
NK040(thi)025:226: de na yang bcad khams gcig yi dam la'o //
NK040(thi)025:228: zhal zas tshogs kyi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK040(thi)025:229: stong gsum tsam du dpe blangs zhing //
NK040(thi)025:230: srid gsum tsam gyis bkang byas pa //
NK040(thi)025:232: rgya mtsho tsam du me re re //
NK040(thi)025:233: gling bzhi tsam du kyi li li //
NK040(thi)025:234: dngos grub stsol ba'i yi dam lha //
NK040(thi)025:235: khyod tshogs la dga' gong bzhin sogs 'grel ma h+aa su kha sa ma ya ho /
NK040(thi)025:236: yi dam rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs 'khor dang
NK040(thi)025:237: bcas pa rnams kyi zhal du g+ha na tsa kra
NK040(thi)025:239: bdag gi dam tshig chags nyams thams cad byang zhing
NK040(thi)025:240: dag nas mchog thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus
NK040(thi)025:242: ces brjod la yi dam gtor ma la 'bul lo //
NK040(thi)025:245: zhal zas tshogs kyi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK040(thi)025:246: stong gsum tsam du dpe blangs zhing //
NK040(thi)025:247: srid gsum tsam gyis bkang byas pa //
NK040(thi)025:248: ri rab tsam du 'u ru ru //
NK040(thi)025:249: rgya mtsho tsam gling bzhi tsam du byin gyis brlab pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)025:251: ye shes dang las la grub pa'i dpa' bo mkha'
NK040(thi)025:252: 'gro shugs 'gro bye ba dung phyur tshogs dang bcas
NK040(thi)025:253: pa rnams kyi zhal du ga na tsa kra puts+tsha
NK040(thi)025:254: me g+ha kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK040(thi)025:255: bdag gi dam tshig chags nyams thams cad byang zhing
NK040(thi)025:256: dag nas mchog thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus
NK040(thi)025:259: de nas chos skyong la 'bul ste /
NK040(thi)025:261: zhal zas tshogs kyis mchod pa 'di //
NK040(thi)025:262: stong gsum tsam du dpe blangs shing //
NK040(thi)025:263: srid gsum tsam gyis bkang byas pa //
NK040(thi)025:264: ri rab tsam du 'u ru ru //
NK040(thi)025:265: rgya mtsho tsam du me re re //
NK040(thi)025:266: gling bzhi tsam du kyi li li //
NK040(thi)025:267: mthu rtsal can gyi chos skyong dang //
NK040(thi)025:268: phrin las bsgrub pa'i dam can rnams //
NK040(thi)025:269: khyed tshogs la dga' sogs nas /
NK040(thi)025:270: sangs rgyas kyis bstan pa bsrung bar zhal gyis bzhes pa'i dam pa chos skyong ba'i srung ma /
NK040(thi)025:271: dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams kyi
NK040(thi)025:272: zhal du g+ha na tsa kra puts+tsha me g+ha kha
NK040(thi)025:273: kha kha hi / bdag gis dam tshigs chags nyams
NK040(thi)025:274: thams cad dag cing byang nas mchog dang thun mong
NK040(thi)025:275: gi dngos grub ma lus pa stsal du gsol /
NK040(thi)025:276: ces brjod la chos skyong gtor ma bcug go //
NK040(thi)025:280: de nas snod cig tu tshogs bcad khams gcig bcug /
NK040(thi)025:281: phud rgod bran la bsham ste /
NK040(thi)025:283: rdo rje'i lta ba bsal ba ni /
NK040(thi)025:285: phyi snod 'jig rten gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)025:286: nang bcud sems can sogs gdan thog gcig ma'i nang ltar 'gres /
NK040(thi)025:287: sarba dz+ny+aa na lo ka g+ha na tsa kra la kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK040(thi)025:288: ces bsngo la phud rgod phyogs bcur gtor /
NK040(thi)025:289: de nas rnal 'byor pa rnams spro dga' dang bcas pas /
NK040(thi)025:291: rjes su lhag ma snod gcig bsdus la /
NK040(thi)025:297: srid gsum b+han+d+ha yangs pa'i gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)025:298: lhag ma'i phung po ri rab gling bzhi tsam //
NK040(thi)025:299: 'dod chags khrag gi rgya mtsho kyi li li //
NK040(thi)025:300: zhe sdang rus pa'i phung po khra la la //
NK040(thi)025:301: gti mug sha yi lhu dum nyi li li //
NK040(thi)025:302: bdud rtsi lnga yi longs spyod bsam mi khyab //
NK040(thi)025:303: 'khor du gtogs pa'i d+aak+ki dam can dang //
NK040(thi)025:304: sdong grogs mdzad pa'i lha srin sde brgyad dang //
NK040(thi)025:305: phyi nang bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad bcu'i tshogs //
NK040(thi)025:306: bka' yi pha 'bab lhag gtor 'di bzhes la //
NK040(thi)025:307: ci ltar bcol ba'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK040(thi)025:308: umo u tsi ta b+ha ling+ta b+hak+sha si s+w+aa h+aa /
NK040(thi)025:309: lhag ma dbang ba'i 'byung po nam mkha'i mtha' dang
NK040(thi)025:310: mnyams pa'i sems can thams cad tshim par gyur cig
NK040(thi)025:312: de nas gtor gzhong chus la chu 'bru gsum gyi bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor byin gyis brlabs la /
NK040(thi)025:313: bstan ma rnams la bsngo ba ni /
NK040(thi)025:315: dgung sngon g.ya' ri gangs rtse dang //
NK040(thi)025:316: spangs ljong dang ni bskyed mos tshal //
NK040(thi)025:317: mtsho dang ne'u seng la gnas pa'i //
NK040(thi)025:318: bdud mo bzhi dang sman mo bzhi //
NK040(thi)025:319: gnod sbyin chen mo bzhi la sogs //
NK040(thi)025:320: bod khams skyong ba'i bstan ma rnams //
NK040(thi)025:321: lhab lhub mang po'i rgyan dang bcas //
NK040(thi)025:322: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang bcas //
NK040(thi)025:323: 'dir byon bshal chu'i gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK040(thi)025:324: dam bskang bcol pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK040(thi)025:325: zhes bshal chu phyi rol gtsang sar dor ro //
NK040(thi)025:326: gtor gzhong kha sbub zhing dgra bgegs 'gug gzhugs drag tu byas la /
NK040(thi)025:329: dbus kyi phyogs nas gro byung ba //
NK040(thi)025:330: sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro'i bro brdung pas //
NK040(thi)025:331: dpa' bo'i bro brdung khrigs se khrig /
NK040(thi)025:332: dpa' mo'i gar byed khyugs se khyug /
NK040(thi)025:333: dgra bgegs phye mar btang ba'i bro //
NK040(thi)025:334: nad gdon thal bar brlag pa'i bro //
NK040(thi)025:338: shar gyi phyogs nas bro byung bas //
NK040(thi)025:339: rdo rje mkha' 'gro'i bro brdung bas //
NK040(thi)025:340: dpa' bo'i dpa' mo'i dgra bgegs bro 'og mnan 'og h'u /
NK040(thi)025:341: lho yi phyogs nas bro byung bas //
NK040(thi)025:342: rin chen mkha' 'gro'i bro brdung pas //
NK040(thi)025:343: dpa' bo'i dpa' mo'i dgra bgegs nad gdon bro 'og mnan 'og h'u /
NK040(thi)025:344: nub kyi phyogs nas bro byung bas //
NK040(thi)025:346: dpa' bo'i dpa' mo'i dgra bgegs nad gdon bro 'og mnan 'og h'u /
NK040(thi)025:347: byang gi phyogs nas bro byung bas //
NK040(thi)025:348: las kyi mkha' 'gro'i bro brdung pas //
NK040(thi)025:349: dpa' bo'i bro brdung khrigs se khrig /
NK040(thi)025:350: dpa' mo'i gar byed khyugs se khyug /
NK040(thi)025:351: dgra bgegs phye mar btags pa'i bro //
NK040(thi)025:352: nad gdon thal bar brlag pa'i bro //
NK040(thi)025:355: lam h'u lam s+t+wam b+ha ya nan /
NK040(thi)025:356: bskal pa'i bar mi thar bar bsam /
NK040(thi)025:357: dkyil 'khor bsdu la las kyi rjes mi mngon par bya'o //
NK040(thi)025:358: pan+di ta don yod rdo rje'i mdzad pa'i gzhung dang /
NK040(thi)025:359: sangs rgyas mnyen ston gyi mdzad pa'i tshogs la brten nas /
